-- Bear Stearns says NYSE OKs share issue to JPMorgan
-- 
-- Fri Apr 4, 2008 7:33pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/04/04/us-bearstearns-jpmorgan-idUSWNAS693320080404

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Bear Stearns Cos BSC.N said on Friday the New York Stock Exchange had approved its request to issue 95 million shares to JPMorgan Chase & Co ( JPM.N ), which is acquiring the investment bank. 

 The stock is being issued as part of a share exchange agreement with JPMorgan, Bear Stearns said. The transaction is expected to close April 8, Bear Stearns said. (Reporting by  Paritosh Bansal ; editing by Carol Bishopric)